    <item>
      <title>如果特朗普发起贸易战，加拿大将采取广泛关税报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/canada-plots-broad-tariff-retaliation-if-trump-starts-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，如果唐纳德·特朗普兑现对加拿大产品征收 25% 关税的威胁，加拿大正制定计划，对美国产品征收大规模关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/canada-plots-broad-tariff-retaliation-if-trump-starts-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:38:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将支持德拉吉关于落后于美国和中国的警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/eu-set-to-back-draghi-warnings-on-lagging-behind-us-and-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份报告草案显示，欧盟将发出警告称，欧盟单一市场的一体化进程正在放缓，同时它还面临着来自美国和中国等全球主要经济体越来越大的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/eu-set-to-back-draghi-warnings-on-lagging-behind-us-and-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>六张图表告诉你英国今年的糟糕开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/uk-bond-yields-borrowing-costs-ramp-up-pressure-on-rachel-reeves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对英国财政状况感到担忧，英国资产在新年伊始遭遇了可怕的开局，这再次唤起了人们对 2022 年导致前首相利兹·特拉斯下台的市场危机的记忆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/uk-bond-yields-borrowing-costs-ramp-up-pressure-on-rachel-reeves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 最高法院之争将言论自由与美国安全对立起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/tiktok-supreme-court-clash-pits-free-speech-against-us-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[广受欢迎的社交媒体平台 TikTok 的未来取决于美国最高法院的一场冲突，这场冲突是国家安全与言论自由之间的冲突，也是一位总统与另一位总统之间的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/tiktok-supreme-court-clash-pits-free-speech-against-us-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芯片制造中心台湾考虑从美国购买更多能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/chipmaking-hub-taiwan-mulls-buying-more-energy-from-the-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾正考虑从美国购买更多能源，以满足国内工业日益增长的需求，台湾政府正在寻找加强与美国关系的方法，并可能避免当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/chipmaking-hub-taiwan-mulls-buying-more-energy-from-the-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 10:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
